  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n- [x] **ISSUE 1**\r\n\r\nIf the User receives a message in a new 1-1 chat on the primary device before pairing, then after pairing this chat will disappear from the activity center on both devices until the sender sends another message\r\nAlso, in this case, the first sent message is not displayed in the chat history on the receiver's devices.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n1. UserA recovers the same account on device1 and device2\r\n2. UserB sends a message in 1-1 chat with UserA (on both devices of UserA the unread indicator appears as expected)\r\n3. UserA syncs device1 and device2 (tick check boxes, press the `Sync all devices` button :) ) without opening the activity center, navigates to the home screen, and opens the activity center (it's empty, which is not expected)\r\n4. UserB sends another message to the 1-1\r\n5. UserA checks the activity center again\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/67952253/144451519-f4c53bf7-3a22-4b8d-90c8-c6c1090b5b59.MP4\r\n\r\n- [x] **ISSUE 2**\r\n\r\nIf the user has two synced devices and leaves a group chat on one of the devices, then the group admin will receive two system messages `[User] left the group`. If one of the devices is offline, then the second system message will come to the group admin as soon as it returns online.\r\n\r\n**Reproduction:**\r\n\r\n1. UserA syncs device1 and device2\r\n2. UserB adds UserA to contacts and creates a group chat\r\n3. UserA joins the group\r\n4. UserA leaves the group\r\n5. UserB checks system messages in the group\r\n\r\n<img width=\"236\" alt=\"Screenshot 2021-12-02 at 16 28 09\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/67952253/144451858-ea0fe3e7-0f46-4f8f-ab9c-ca6eb624fc19.png\">\r\n\r\n- [x] **ISSUE 3** \r\n\r\nIf the user joins the group chat before pairing, that group will disappear from the primary device after pairing.\r\n\r\n**Reproduction:**\r\n\r\n1. UserA recovers the same account on device1 and device2\r\n2. UserB creates a group chat with UserA\r\n3. UserA joins the group on device1 (UserB receives the system message in the group UserA joined the group)\r\n4. UserA syncs device1 and device2 (UserB receives the system message in the group UserA left the group)\r\n5. UserA checks the home screen on device1 (the group chat disappeared) and the activity center on device2 (the group chat is still there, but nothing happens for UserB and device1 when pressing Join on device2)\r\n\r\n**Expected result:** the group chat appears on the home screen on device2 after pairing, UserA is a member\r\n\r\ncc @bitgamma ",
